Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.configuration

The configuration of the template engine.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Configuration
    Contains all dynamic parts of the template engine.
    ConfigurationElement
    A part of a configuration.
    ConfigurationElementCustomiser
    Customises a configuration element after it has been created.
    ConfigurationElementFactory
    Creates configuration elements (except for the factory itself).
  • Class Summary

    ConfigurationParameters
    Initialisation parameters of a configuration.
    DefaultConfiguration
    A default configuration.
    DefaultConfigurationElementFactory
    The default configuration element factory implementation.

Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.configuration Description

The configuration of the template engine. Please see the wiki page for information about configuring Aluminum.
